<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Apply to ba Guest - MESH Club</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/apply-as-guest.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/logo.png" type="image/x-icon">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="hero-image">
        <h1>Become a Guest Speaker at MESH Club, IIT Jammu</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="intro">
        <h3>Share Your Knowledge, Inspire the Next Generation</h3>
        <p>Welcome to the MESH Club at IIT Jammu's Guest Speaker Application page! We are dedicated to bringing industry experts, thought leaders, and innovators to interact with our students and share their invaluable insights. If you have expertise in your field and a passion for inspiring young minds, we would love to have you as a guest speaker at our upcoming events.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>Why Join Us as a Guest Speaker?</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><span>Impact Future Innovators:</span> Speak to a highly motivated audience of students and faculty eager to learn from the best in the industry.</li>
            <li><span>Platform for Knowledge Sharing:</span> Share your expertise, ideas, and experiences with the future leaders of technology, entrepreneurship, and more.</li>
            <li><span>Create Meaningful Connections:</span> As a speaker, you will have the chance to interact with students, faculty, and professionals from various domains.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>Types of Sessions we Host?</h3>
        <p>At MESH Club, we organize a variety of events where guest speakers can contribute:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><span>Guest Lectures:</span> In-depth sessions on specific topics of expertise.</li>
            <li><span>Workshops & Seminars:</span> Interactive sessions where students can learn practical skills.</li>
            <li><span>Panel Discussions:</span> Group discussions with industry experts on current trends or challenges.</li>
            <li><span>Networking Events:</span> Opportunities for students to engage with experts and explore collaborations.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>Who can apply?</h3>
        <p>We invite professionals from various industries and fields to apply. Whether you are an expert in technology, business, social impact, or research, your experience can make a difference to our students.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Researchers, academicians, and innovators</li>
            <li>Entrepreneurs and startup founders</li>
            <li>Leaders in emerging technologies (AI, Blockchain, Robotics, etc.)</li>
            <li>Experts in social impact, sustainability, and leadership</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>How to apply?</h3>
        <p>Interested in becoming a guest speaker at MESH Club? It's simple! Just follow the steps below:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><span>Fill out the Application Form:</span> Please provide us with your details and expertise.</li>
            <li><span>Submit your Proposal:</span> Briefly describe the topic(s) you would like to speak on and why it would be beneficial for our students.</li>
            <li><span>Review Process:</span> Our team will get back to you within 7 business days.</li>
            <li><span>Confirm Your Session:</span> We'll schedule a session that fits your availability and our event calendar.</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/google-form-link" class="apply-btn"><button>Apply Now</button></a>
    </div>

    <p class="note"><span>Note:</span> We respect your privacy. All the information you provide in the application will only be used for event planning purposes.</p>


    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
